snippet.title: Keelvin
snippet.description:
Hey, Keelvin here! AKA Vincal, AKA Notch’s son!
You may know me from my let's plays, live streams, shorts, memes or from the church of holes. There's a lot going on here.
Now hit subscribe to enter the hole and join the religion! (You also get pretty epic videos)

I don't have a stream schedule so ringing the bell or following my socials is the best way to be notified:
Discord: https://discord.gg/GgJEzGRyAd
Twitter: https://twitter.com/VincalHolmes

I mostly stream here on YouTube but I stream on Twitch occasionally: https://www.twitch.tv/vincalholmes

Thats all, have a happy Tuesday!
